headline: Palantir Crushes 63% Growth While UiPath Celebrates Its First Profit
summary: UiPath (NYSE: PATH) and Palantir Technologies (Nasdaq: PLTR) both beat Q3 estimates, but the results reveal fundamentally different AI business models. UiPath turned its first GAAP profit on automation software that executes tasks. Palantir posted 63% revenue growth on analytics software that interprets data.
